name: Oracle

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond:
EXISTS(SELECT * FROM IBZDCSYSTEM t21 
 WHERE 
 t11.PSSYSTEMID = t21.SYSTEMID  AND  ( t21.SRFDCID = #{ctx.sessioncontext.srfdcid}  AND  ( t21.SYSPERMISSION IS NULL  OR  t21.SYSPERMISSION = 'ALL' ) ) )
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

queryCode:
SELECT
t1.APPCATEGORY,
t1.APPWFS,
t1.CODENAME,
t1.CREATEDATE,
t1.CREATEMAN,
t1.ICON,
t1.ICONCSS,
t1.INDEXCODENAME,
t1.MOBILEAPP,
t1.PSSYSTEMAPPID,
t1.PSSYSTEMAPPNAME,
t1.SERVICEID,
t1.SHOWORDER,
t1.SYSTEMID,
t1.TIP,
t1.UPDATEDATE,
t1.UPDATEMAN,
t1.URL,
t1.VIEWPATHFORMAT
FROM IBZPSSYSTEMAPP t1 
LEFT JOIN IBZPSSYSTEM t11 ON t1.SYSTEMID = t11.PSSYSTEMID
